[106371017911437766410,100408081424595912004,Palmer Square is a an excellent resource for the thousands living within walking distance of this wide park. The Square is bordered by small Chicago mansions and is threaded with walking paths and rolling turf, sports a playground, and has plenty of trees for shade. It is a popular running spot and dog walk year-round, but in the spring and summer you'll find dozens of locals lazing in the grass with books or blankets, dozing, picnicking, and enjoying the view. An essential part of the Logan Square living experience.]
